### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### LEARNING PLATFORM API TEST REQUESTS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### VARIABLES
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api

# Organization & Resource IDs
@orgId = org-123
@orgSlug = my-org
@courseId = course-123
@courseSlug = math-101
@classId = class-456
@userId = user-456
@studentId = student-789
@groupId = group-123

# Lesson/Homework Node IDs
@lessonNodeId = lesson-123
@moduleId = module-123
@homeworkId = homework-123
@classLessonNodeId = classLessonNode-123

# Test user credentials
@testEmail = testuser@example.com
@testPassword = Test@123456
@testName = Test User

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### AUTHENTICATION (RUN THESE FIRST!)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 1. Sign Up (tạo user mới)
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/sign-up/email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{testEmail}}",
  "password": "{{testPassword}}",
  "name": "{{testName}}"
}

### 2. Sign In (đăng nhập để lấy session)
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/sign-in/email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{testEmail}}",
  "password": "{{testPassword}}"
}

### 3. Get Current Session (kiểm tra session hiện tại)
GET {{apiUrl}}/auth/session

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 1. HEALTH CHECK
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Health Check
GET {{apiUrl}}/health

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 2. COURSES API
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get all courses in organization
GET {{apiUrl}}/courses?organizationId={{orgId}}

### Get course by slug
GET {{apiUrl}}/courses/by-slug/{{orgSlug}}/{{courseSlug}}

### Create a new course
POST {{apiUrl}}/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mathematics 101",
  "slug": "math-101",
  "organizationId": "{{orgId}}",
  "description": "Introduction to Mathematics"
}

### Add lesson node (module/lesson/homework)
POST {{apiUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/nodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parentId": "{{moduleId}}",
  "type": "lesson",
  "title": "Lesson 1: Introduction",
  "content": {
    "text": "This is the lesson content",
    "widgets": []
  }
}

### Update lesson node
PATCH {{apiUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/nodes/{{lessonNodeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Lesson Title",
  "content": {
    "text": "Updated lesson content",
    "widgets": []
  }
}

### Delete lesson node
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/nodes/{{lessonNodeId}}

### Reorder lesson node
PATCH {{apiUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/nodes/{{lessonNodeId}}/reorder
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetParentId": "{{moduleId}}",
  "targetIndex": 2
}

### Get homework status
GET {{apiUrl}}/courses/homework-status?courseId={{courseId}}&classId={{classId}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 3. CLASSES API
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get user's classes (grouped by role)
GET {{apiUrl}}/classes

### Get class with course data
GET {{apiUrl}}/classes/{{classId}}

### Create a new class
POST {{apiUrl}}/classes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Class 10A",
  "courseId": "{{courseId}}",
  "organizationId": "{{orgId}}"
}

### Add member to class
POST {{apiUrl}}/classes/{{classId}}/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "role": "student"
}

### Get class students
GET {{apiUrl}}/classes/{{classId}}/students

### Get student's pending assignments
GET {{apiUrl}}/classes/{{classId}}/pending-assignments

### Get pending assignments for multiple classes (batch)
POST {{apiUrl}}/classes/pending-assignments-batch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "classIds": ["{{classId}}", "class-789", "class-101"]
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 4. USERS API
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Find user by email
GET {{apiUrl}}/users/search?email={{testEmail}}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 5. MEMBERS API
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Check if user belongs to organization (by orgId)
GET {{apiUrl}}/members/check?orgId={{orgId}}

### Check if user belongs to organization (by orgSlug)
GET {{apiUrl}}/members/check?orgSlug={{orgSlug}}

### Add member to organization
POST {{apiUrl}}/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "organizationId": "{{orgId}}",
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "role": "member"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 6. CLASS GROUPS API
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get groups in class
GET {{apiUrl}}/class-groups/{{classId}}

### Create a group
POST {{apiUrl}}/class-groups/{{classId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Group A",
  "description": "First working group"
}

### Add student to group
POST {{apiUrl}}/class-groups/{{groupId}}/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "{{studentId}}"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 7. CLASS LESSON NODES API
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Load class lesson nodes
GET {{apiUrl}}/class-lesson-nodes?lessonNodeId={{lessonNodeId}}&classId={{classId}}

### Get counts of class lesson nodes
POST {{apiUrl}}/class-lesson-nodes/counts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lessonNodeIds": ["{{lessonNodeId}}", "lesson-456"],
  "classId": "{{classId}}"
}

### Add class lesson node (lesson_note or homework_imp)
POST {{apiUrl}}/class-lesson-nodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lessonNodeId": "{{lessonNodeId}}",
  "classId": "{{classId}}",
  "type": "lesson_note",
  "content": {
    "text": "My lesson notes",
    "attachments": []
  }
}

### Delete class lesson node
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/class-lesson-nodes/{{classLessonNodeId}}?classId={{classId}}

### Get build run ID for lesson node
GET {{apiUrl}}/class-lesson-nodes/{{lessonNodeId}}/build-run

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 8. WIDGETS API
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get all widgets
GET {{apiUrl}}/widgets

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### TIPS:
### - Replace @variables with actual IDs when testing
### - Ensure backend is running on http://localhost:3000
### - Run authentication endpoints first to get session
### - Use Ctrl+Alt+R (or Cmd+Alt+R on Mac) to send request
